{"tid":1386963,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭奧大香港女生校園設連儂牆　遭內地生推撞倒地","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T15:03:46.000Z","uid":66271,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"61e323be6042d9735478efa76912601cbfa563d1","tid":1386963,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3097441/org/020d4bdec675a8874505aa3ae6b3d474.jpg/JwSBnnDYPuPFXrr_YMNvhW6K9AFqzRhvWtHxuVrR8bk?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3097441%2Forg%2F020d4bdec675a8874505aa3ae6b3d474.jpg%2FJwSBnnDYPuPFXrr_YMNvhW6K9AFqzRhvWtHxuVrR8bk%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=0a7d7160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆遍地開花，不少香港留學生亦在外地校園設立連儂牆，表達對事件的關注。繼澳洲昆士蘭大學後，紐西蘭奧克蘭大學（The University of Auckland）再有中國學生衝撞香港學生事件。facebook專頁「New Zealand Hong Konger」昨日上載影片，只見香港學生設置連儂牆期間，一批中國留學生上前質問並推撞其中一名女生至倒下。<br />\n<br />\n涉事香港學生向《香港01》表示，連儂牆目前已被拆除，現以聯署方式向奧克蘭大學表達不滿，校方亦回覆指會調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3096549/org/dad6f6a9dd7a075093993005cde868cd.jpg/9oVXbbq76Vc175VmEVm1OHZDOGnQl0IDM2Y7kjNmO5I?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3096549%2Forg%2Fdad6f6a9dd7a075093993005cde868cd.jpg%2F9oVXbbq76Vc175VmEVm1OHZDOGnQl0IDM2Y7kjNmO5I%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1a4ab504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wx9OgGDTNZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dwx9OgGDTNZM&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCueQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=df13918a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wx9OgGDTNZM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89aad02517862b640939181b63b619feee133fc8","tid":1386963,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike